    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>getRegionList returns all territories which are contained within CLDR.</p>

<p>It was told that a function which returns only countries and only continents would be nice.
Also a function which returns what countries are included in an continent should be included.</p>

<p>Proposed new functions:</p>

<p>getCountryList() - only countries, no territories
getTerritoryList() - some are not continents... f.e. oceania or middle east
getTerritoryDetail() - for which countrys are included in an territory</p>

